OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777978996
OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FThat allowed her to be sentenced to
OL,7,Fone day in jail, which the judge said
OL,8,Fshe served when she was booked, one
OL,9,Fyear of probation, a required DUI
OL,10,Fclass and state-mandated fines.
OL,12,FThe plea offer was standard for
OL,13,Fdefendants with no DUI history, no
OL,14,Fcrash or injury on the road, and a low
OL,15,Fblood-alcohol level, the county
OL,16,Fdistrict attorney's office said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
