OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777978996
OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FAnd it's especially common for
OL,7,Fdefendants who have shown motivation
OL,8,Fto address their problems and seek
OL,9,Ftreatment, as Spears did when she
OL,10,Fvoluntarily checked in to a substance
OL,11,Fabuse treatment centre last month.
OL,13,F"I don't think anybody's happy about
OL,14,Fpleading guilty to anything, but under
OL,15,Fthe circumstances, to get this behind
OL,16,Fher, I think everybody is pleased with
OL,17,Fthe result," Goldstein said after the
OL,18,Fhearing.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
