OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FShe temporarily waives her Fourth
OL,7,FAmendment search-and-seizure rights if
OL,8,Fshe is pulled over, meaning she must
OL,9,Fautomatically submit to searches and
OL,10,Fsobriety tests.
OL,12,FAt Goldstein's request, the judge
OL,13,Fruled this would not apply to her home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
