OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FShe was charged on Thursday with one
OL,7,Fmisdemeanour DUI count, which meant
OL,8,Fshe was not required to appear in
OL,9,Fcourt for her arraignment.
OL,11,FBut her representatives hadn't said
OL,12,Fwhether she would appear, and the
OL,13,Fhearing drew an unusually heavy media
OL,14,Fturnout for Ventura, a seaside city of
OL,15,Fabout 110,000 people roughly 70 miles
OL,16,F(113 kilometres) northwest of downtown
OL,17,FLA.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
