OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FAfter her March 4 arrest, a
OL,7,Frepresentative called her actions
OL,8,Finexcusable and said that ideally, the
OL,9,Farrest would lead to overdue change in
OL,10,Fher life.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FShe was pulled over for driving her
OL,18,Fblack BMW quickly and erratically on
OL,19,FU.S. 101, the California Highway
OL,20,FPatrol said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
