OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FShe appeared to be impaired, took a
OL,7,Fseries of field sobriety tests, was
OL,8,Farrested and was taken to jail, the
OL,9,FCHP said.
OL,11,FAuthorities said in the criminal
OL,12,Fcomplaint that Spears had alcohol and
OL,13,Fdrugs in her system, but they didn't
OL,14,Fspecify which drugs or list her blood
OL,15,Falcohol content.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
