OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FSpears grew to superstardom in the
OL,7,F1990s and 2000s with hits including
OL,8,F"Toxic," "Gimme More" and "I'm a Slave
OL,9,F4 U." Most of her nine studio albums
OL,10,Fhave been certified platinum, with two
OL,11,Fdiamond titles: 1999's "... Baby One
OL,12,FMore Time" and 2000s "Oops! ... I Did
OL,13,FIt Again."
OL,15,FShe became a tabloid obsession in the
OL,16,Fearly 2000s and a source of intense
OL,17,Fpublic scrutiny as she battled mental
OL,18,Fillness, and paparazzi fought to
OL,19,Fdocument the details of her private
OL,20,Flife.
