OL,3,CBritney Spears avoids jail after
OL,4,Cpleading guilty to lesser DUI charge
OL,6,FIn 2008, Spears was placed under a
OL,7,Fcourt-ordered conservatorship, run
OL,8,Fprimarily by her father and his
OL,9,Flawyers, that would control her
OL,10,Fpersonal and financial decisions for
OL,11,Fwell over a decade. It was dissolved
OL,12,Fin 2021.
OL,14,FSince then, she has married, divorced,
OL,15,Fand released a bestselling memoir,
OL,16,F"The Woman in Me."
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@RO]
